  "name": "Gawker Kinja Fixes",
  "description": "Fixes a few annoying things about the new layout. Choose yes or no for each.\r\n\r\n1.Thumbnail Scrolling: Makes all the images small when scrolling the 'latest' and 'recommended' pages\r\n\r\n2.Normal Image Size: Makes story image normal size instead of huge (haven't got this working for vids yet)\r\n\r\n3.Hide Annotations: Hides the black pointy things on images\r\n\r\n4.Un-grey Comments: Gives unapproved comments the same background and text colour as approved comments \r\n\r\n5.Retro Logo: Change logo to retro style\r\n\r\nTo apply this to all the Gawker sites go <a href=\"http://userstyles.org/styles/86519/kinja-fixes?r=1366818549\">here</a>\r\n\r\nSee also <a href=\"http://userstyles.org/styles/85846/jezebel-kinja-fixes?r=1366631007\">Jezebel Kinja Fixes</a>, <a href=\"http://userstyles.org/styles/84880/retro-gawker\">Retro Gawker</a>",
